state.title: Building
state.tooltip: Each building will have different effects once built. For example, they can affect units, wealth, repression or public happiness.||By viewing these effects you can choose buildings that will provide the biggest boosts to the areas you want.||If the building is damaged it will cease to provide the effects until repaired.||Move your cursor over the effects icons for more details.

uiEntry.title: Text
uiEntry.script: function InitState(state) Component.Call("Resize", Component.Call("Width"), state.Text.DisplayHeight) Component.Call("Parent.LuaCall", "SetTextExtents", state.Text.DisplayWidth, state.Text.DisplayHeight) end

uiEntry.script:
function OnLeaveDepress() local parent = Component.GetProperty("ParentPopup") Component.Call("Root.LuaCall", "ClosePopup", parent) end
function SetParentPopupAddress(addr) print("Setting parent address: "..tostring(addr)) Component.SetProperty("ParentPopup", addr) end
